Package brave.jaxrs2

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ContainerParser
    JAX-RS specific type used to customize traced requests based on the JAX-RS resource.
    SpanCustomizingContainerFilter
    Adds application-tier data to an existing http span via ContainerParser.
    TracingClientFilter
    This filter is set at highest priority which means it executes before other filters.
